## Related Projects / 关联项目

**kpop-design-system** (https://github.com/SuanFishXYY/kpop-design-system) —
姊妹项目，复用本仓库的安装器架构和治理体系，新增 97 位 K-pop idol UI agent。
Sister project that reuses this repo's installer architecture and governance
lineage, adds 97 K-pop idol UI agents.

两个项目共享：Bug #1-#9 治理史、虚拟环境沙箱、虚拟机装机规约、6 大 CLI 适配层。
Both projects share: Bug #1-#9 remediation history, virtual sandbox testing,
virgin-machine install conventions, 6-CLI compatibility layer.